{"tid":663784,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"天涯 的盡頭是風沙 紅塵 的故事叫牽掛","createTime":"2018-05-13T14:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T16:42:42.000Z","uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d71dc447e583569c106cfb5d5ba1330e39b0f8d9","tid":663784,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"檐下 窗櫺斜映枝椏<br />\n與你 席地對座飲茶<br />\n我以工筆畫將你牢牢 的記下<br />\n提筆 不為風雅<br />\n<br />\n燈下 嘆紅顏近晚霞<br />\n我說緣份 一如參禪不說話<br />\n你淚如梨花灑滿了紙上的天下<br />\n愛恨如寫意 山水畫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方文山究竟食咩大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n填到啲詞好似首詩咁<br />\n仲要有意景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68eed4f824c1c80d4f9aae22a0b5a298b39a46ce","tid":663784,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"好強"},{"pid":"3966afcab78c76bdfacac6bb88b10a842b895178","tid":663784,"uid":27513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VCGc1u6Dm7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVCGc1u6Dm7E&d=fDtbx6VS4Ev2Tg%2FMxdVZCAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b622aae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VCGc1u6Dm7E</a>"},{"pid":"b63770a65207a90e67bcbe39b0a1b898ae04fbb3","tid":663784,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3966afcab78c76bdfacac6bb88b10a842b895178","tid":663784,"uid":27513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VCGc1u6Dm7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVCGc1u6Dm7E&d=fDtbx6VS4Ev2Tg%2FMxdVZCAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D